{"tid":1369654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴重警告，唔好圍教會","createTime":"2019-07-26T18:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T18:24:19.000Z","uid":136686,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"21e5c61bfe9c054cb0252eb43739c7458a90d01c","tid":1369654,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚴重警告，唔好圍教會</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚴重警告，唔好圍教會</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚴重警告，唔好圍教會</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一陣教會閂門唔比入唔好喊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1366685\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1366685</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然親中教會係仆街<br />\n但佢地同循道衛理，好鄰里教會<br />\n等等支援群眾活動嘅教會，信嘅係同一個基督教<br />\n<br />\n雖然宗派可能唔同，但大家都係主內弟兄<br />\n咁主內弟兄出事，教會之間就被逼要幫佢地<br />\n<br />\n圍親中教會只會令親群眾教會難做<br />\n你搞教會，魔攻團同戰地崇拜都會受壓而停辦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宗教問題宗教解決<br />\n教外人士唔好攻擊任何教會</span></span>"},{"pid":"8ba1513cf5f767ca93792e66ba0cafc0e4f7ddea","tid":1369654,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8bc6f853870f0b8a25e258bb7e2cc06982d86f5","tid":1369654,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a902667a2c903a3f6d01d3f585aae2e3b4cedee","tid":1369654,"uid":136686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204c1c8f19ef145838400f4858a96af13263ef86","tid":1369654,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e811e9e981bb17b05f8fe748a4216f953470bd5